":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ac32d3e550d63e8132854092766c9991d0cb94","tid":1764330,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d474298693029279baf95c8e5c56be87958d25df","tid":1764330,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20191201/20816192\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F20816192&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=870e133f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fspecial%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F20816192&h=db78e082\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20191201/20816192</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】理大游繩逃生慘烈20分鐘 難民拯救隊──鐵騎家長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191201/large/1575027924_5797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575027924_5797.jpg&h=6f196237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n千鈞一髮間，抗爭者魚貫地游繩逃出理大，再陸續坐上電單車。<br />\n<br />\n鐵騎士敏捷不羈的身影，帶領手足飛馳公路的驚險情節，最近在兩場大學保衞戰中成為了焦點。先是位置偏僻的中文大學，私家車在擠擁山路中寸步難行，電單車手繞過路障傳送物資則輕而易舉；後來理工大學被重兵圍堵，警察喪呼要「六四重演」，電單車手遂趕到漆咸道南天橋，在這個「無警」缺口突圍營救，接應游繩爬下來的手足。<br />\n<br />\n「就算紅磡附近有很多警察，我都不畏懼。我已沒有任何希望，我只希望每一個手足可以安全回家。」MaTi（化名）是理工大學營救行動中的一位電單車手，他憶述拯救行動僅為時20分鐘，即被警察發現腰斬，此後的10分鐘可謂千鈞一髮，趕急帶領游繩下來的手足逃亡。逃脫以後，MaTi並未鬆懈，每天都在理大附近等待奇蹟再發生，但抗爭者已無法再突圍，「七日過後，再沒有等到任何消息。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191201/large/1575027921_2ea5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575027921_2ea5.jpg&h=6d4376c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191201/large/1575027922_2abc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575027922_2abc.jpg&h=73a67cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少示威者游繩逃脫時擦破雙手，有人掌心潰爛。互聯網"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:30:47.000Z","msg":"要戴手套"},{"pid":"30c406b36a583254e402cf322cb504271850c912","tid":1764330,"uid":211993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:32:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e22326b96eafb15598266e7e44c8c0aabfbc8834","tid":1764330,"uid":160537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"無命英雄"},{"pid":"586c3a5082c00a8951d9bbb54998b0158917ef0f","tid":1764330,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d99058288bb5c7f6dd25f6f0ae7856670673def","tid":1764330,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77bf0507a5e2289b1cdfffb126b04264c6fbf31","tid":1764330,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:37:20.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"3c4014fffddf3077426b5a1f6d56e2085ea97044","tid":1764330,"uid":188411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:37:43.000Z